<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_2e7709dc-37d1-4359-9b21-1e94566bdfbe" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>7.3.5</sptc><title id="_a00902cd-ae50-4472-8642-e020088048fb">Anti-ponding device/board</title><archive-num>2019: 3.5.2.5</archive-num><subclause id="_5dac4ea7-6c47-49bf-9268-042b71984ef6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d5c630fa-1fa3-4c5c-b1e4-888c29c4708d">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>An anti-ponding device/board must be provided where sarking is installed on—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e0324035-1cb8-46df-843d-3acf4008279a">roofs with a pitch less than 20°; and</li><li id="_60d35083-7b66-475e-85c9-bdc81809b009">roofs with no eaves overhang, regardless of the roof pitch.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_99b6ed18-e0c9-4ca7-bf95-c6895d47bc8e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_7b3a7878-67ac-475a-9cc2-178046f03cf8">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>An anti-ponding device <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_8d4d68c3-19f9-4144-91be-2137fdffcae7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> by (1) must be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1520_0.5.0.xml#_787642fb-810b-4dc9-8ea9-f54fcfbc19e1" id="_b9221e10-430b-4ac7-b2b8-d5ca693cb644" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">water resistant</xref> and fixed along the eaves line from the top of the fascia back up the rafter with a clearance of approximately 50 mm below the first batten (See <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/677_0.6.0.xml#_c9d89b7f-8fae-46d8-ad48-3d46c177e393" id="_8c588216-ac1d-400d-855f-9788260794c3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 7.3.5</xref>).</p></subclause><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/677_0.6.0.xml" id="_c9d89b7f-8fae-46d8-ad48-3d46c177e393"><num/><title id="_171c36ed-02e5-4c63-8830-6ace5fd66326"/></image-reference></clause>